comments.comment: renqs Any progress on this issue？

Hi hxb. I made a PR that should fix this issue. I think it's connected either with concurrent creating of Project instances from generated code (maybe #newInstance method is not thread-safe) or with race condition during closing of LookupFullCache (currently #close method doesn't wait until the end of active reload, if it's happening). Both of these problems are fixed in the MR.
